text = "~ ~ Memo Project Settings ~ ~

(the goal is that one 'unit' in godot = one character in cluige = same coordinates)

Customize to your project :
Application / Config / Name = \"your game title\"
Application / Run / Max FPS = 15 wanted FPS in cluige and in godot
Display / Window / Size / Viewport Width = 112 characters in cluige
Display / Window / Size / Viewport Height = 60 characters in cluige
Display / Window / Size / Viewport Width Override = 952 pixels in godot run (stretched)
Display / Window / Size / Viewport Height Override = 510 pixels in godot run (stretched)
Rendering / Environment / Defaults / Default Clear Color = what you prefer"
label_settings = ExtResource("1_vo7e0")

